<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ea73df8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s269a"><num value="269a">§ 269a.</num><heading> Central Bureau of the International Map of the World on the Millionth Scale; authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is hereby authorized to be appropriated, out of any money in the Treasury not otherwise appropriated, an annual sum of $50 as a contribution on the part of the United States toward the expenses incurred by the Central Bureau of the International Map of the World on the Millionth Scale.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8ea73df9-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/act/1930-06-27/ch652">June 27, 1930, ch. 652</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/46/825">46 Stat. 825</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
